channel.title: Happy birthday to me
channel.description:
Well, it's been a year since my last birthday topic. What has changed? School is new, I still like the same girl.. Community has changed, I have stayed the same.. Which made people to forget me, most of you probably don't even know me.. Well. Nobody cares anyway. 'Happy birthday to me, happy birthday to me, nobody cares about me, happy birthday to me..' I still remember everyone as I used to, though people have changed. This might be my last post, maybe, maybe not. Who cares anyway? I'm just one person in such a huge community. I guess it is my destiny to be boring guy who nobody remembers.
I've been planning of leaving the cheating scenes, but always when I tried to, I found something which tied to me on the forums. I find this forum the one closest to me, with such friendly people and... Meh. [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,42215.20.html]Link to my old birthday topic[/url]
